890	Introduce timed actions into ckanext-queue	pudo		"The ckan queuing system should provide the option to subscribe to timed re-submissions of specific resources. This could look as follows: 

 * routing_key: Package 
 * operation: daily 
 * payload: pkg.as_dict() 

Where operation is one of daily, weekly, monthly or any other interval. "	enhancement	new	major	ckan-v1.3	ckan					
